## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the role of culture in ethics. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant insights from non-English speaking regions. Additionally, the dynamic nature of culture and ethics means that interpretations and applications can vary widely across different contexts and over time.